---
---

<section id="why-us" class="section why-us">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="why-header">
      <p class="mono-label">WHY US</p>
      <h2 class="why-headline">Not another<br />tour company.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="why-spread">
      <!-- Left: Conservation story with image -->
      <div class="why-story">
        <div class="story-image-wrap">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472396961693-142e6e269027?auto=format&fit=crop&w=960&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472396961693-142e6e269027?auto=format&fit=crop&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472396961693-142e6e269027?auto=format&fit=crop&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472396961693-142e6e269027?auto=format&fit=crop&w=960&q=80 960w"
            sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw"
            alt="Sulawesi forest wildlife"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="story-text">
          <span class="story-label">CONSERVATION</span>
          <p class="story-body">
            A portion of every trip supports protection work in Sulawesi Tengah. No grants, no vague claims, no pressure on guests to participate.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="story-quote">"We protect what's already standing."</blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Big numbered points -->
      <div class="why-reasons">
        <article class="reason">
          <span class="reason-num">01</span>
          <div class="reason-text">
            <h3>No middleman markup</h3>
            <p>You speak with the team running your route in Sulawesi Tengah, not a broker writing from another city.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason">
          <span class="reason-num">02</span>
          <div class="reason-text">
            <h3>No scripted guiding</h3>
            <p>We brief facts clearly, then make room for real conversation when plans, weather, or local events shift the day.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason">
          <span class="reason-num">03</span>
          <div class="reason-text">
            <h3>No hidden fees</h3>
            <p>What you confirm is what you pay. If logistics change, we explain options before money changes hands.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason">
          <span class="reason-num">04</span>
          <div class="reason-text">
            <h3>No tourist-trap detours</h3>
            <p>Partners are locally run families and crews we already know, not forced stops designed for commissions.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-us {
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    padding: 5rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .why-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .why-header .mono-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .why-header .mono-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--text);
  }

  .why-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Spread layout */
  .why-spread {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Story panel */
  .why-story {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .story-image-wrap {
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .story-image-wrap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 40%;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26, 23, 20, 0.4), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .story-image-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 2 / 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: filter 0.4s ease;
  }

  .story-image-wrap:hover img {
    filter: brightness(1.05) saturate(1.1);
  }

  .story-text {
    padding: 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .story-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bg-warm);
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .story-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 4vw, 1.85rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--lime);
  }

  /* Reasons panel */
  .why-reasons {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reason {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 4rem 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    transition: background 0.25s ease, filter 0.25s ease;
  }

  .reason:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    filter: brightness(1.02);
  }

  .reason:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .reason:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .reason-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--light);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .reason:hover .reason-num {
    color: var(--lime);
  }

  .reason-text h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .reason:hover .reason-text h3 {
    color: var(--forest);
  }

  .reason-text p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Large */
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .why-us {
      padding: 6rem 0 7rem;
    }

    .reason {
      grid-template-columns: 4.5rem 1fr;
    }

    .reason-num {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  /* Tablet */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-spread {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .why-story {
      position: static;
    }

    .story-image-wrap img {
      aspect-ratio: 2 / 1;
    }

    .reason {
      grid-template-columns: 3.5rem 1fr;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .reason-num {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .reason-text h3 {
      padding-top: 0.35rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 639px) {
    .why-us {
      padding: 4rem 0 4.5rem;
    }

    .why-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .story-image-wrap img {
      aspect-ratio: 2.5 / 1;
    }

    .reason {
      grid-template-columns: 2.75rem 1fr;
    }

    .reason-num {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .reason:hover {
      background: transparent;
      filter: none;
    }
  }
</style>